dct_title_s: Asia for the elucidation of the Abbe Gaultiers geographical games
dct_description_sm: by Johoshaphat Aspin 1822 ; Hewitt sc. Buckingm. Place.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows, Asia, eastern Africa, and Australia. Africa and Australia exclude interior details.
